NOTICE — combined-work licensing

RF24StageLink is licensed MIT and contains no RF24 source code. However, it is
designed to be compiled and linked against the RF24 library by TMRh20 / J. Coliz,
which is licensed under the GNU General Public License, version 2 (GPL-2.0-only).

Because a typical microcontroller build statically links RF24StageLink and RF24
into a single firmware image, that combined binary you distribute is a derivative
work governed by GPL-2.0-only. The MIT license above applies to the RF24StageLink
source on its own; it does not, and cannot, relax RF24's GPL-2.0-only terms for
the combined firmware. Distribute combined firmware accordingly.
